name: 52north.github.com
body:
### Welcome to 52°North's GitHub

52°North is an open source organization with a strong standing in the geospatial domain. We like to operate on the edge of research and industry, so it is just a natural step to try out GitHub as a hosting service.

Stay tuned for new projects on GitHub and more information at http://52north.org.

### Contact
This test site and the evaluation of GitHub is conducted by @ridoo, @nuest and @matthesrieke - please dont hesitate to get in touch if you have any questions.
